  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
    <subfield code="a">The Yakutsk array group is developing the wide FOV Cherenkov telescope to be operated in coincidence with the surface detectors of the array. Currently the engineering prototype of the reflecting telescope with front-end electronics is designed and assembled to prove the feasibility of an instrument conceived. The status and specifications of the prototype telescope are presented as well as the modernization program of the Cherenkov light detectors subset of the array.</subfield>
  </datafield>
